{"id":179572,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/北京东城区设置“纯居民”限制独立参选人资格-徐/","date":"2011-09-16T07:43:42Z","modified":"2011-09-16T07:43:42Z","title":"北京东城区设置“纯居民”限制独立参选人资格 徐春柳以离职应对","content":"<p>来源：新浪微博</p>\n<p>【东城区独立参选人徐春柳为了应对这个突如其来的&ldquo;纯居民&rdquo;限制，现已准备离职。】</p>\n<p>@东城区徐春柳：<span style=\"color: #444444;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height: 22px;background-color: #d0f1f6\">【向法律专家求助，东城区人大曲解选举法，生造&ldquo;纯居民&rdquo;概念，阻止我进行选民登记】今天早上我去做选民登记，居委会书记称我不是&ldquo;纯居民&rdquo;无法在社区登记。她说区人大有文件，只有户口在小区，失业在家的才是纯居民，我有工作，只能在工作单位登记。这是曲解选举法，选民应是自由选择登记地。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #444444;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;background-color: #d0f1f6\"></p>\n<div class=\"MIB_assign\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 5px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;width: 474px;clear: both;padding: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<div class=\"MIB_assign\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 5px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;width: 474px;clear: both;padding: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<div class=\"MIB_assign_c MIB_txtbl\">\n<div class=\"blogPicOri\" style=\"clear: both;text-align: center;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 6px;padding-left: 0px;text-align: left;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><cite><a href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><img class=\"small_icon cls quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />收起</a> <cite class=\"MIB_line_l\">|</cite> </cite><cite><a href=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/53998985tw1dl73nw03owj.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"small_icon original quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />查看大图</a> </cite><cite class=\"MIB_line_l\">|</cite> <cite><a id=\"left131615881415635880\" href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><img class=\"small_icon turn_l quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />向左转</a> </cite><cite><a id=\"right131615881415655476\" class=\"last_turn_r\" href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><img class=\"small_icon turn_r quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />向右转</a></cite></p>\n<p><img class=\"imgSmall quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/53998985tw1dl73nw03owj.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feed_att MIB_linkbl MIB_txtbl\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;color: #707070;clear: both;width: 560px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<div class=\"lf\" style=\"float: left;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><cite><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1402571141/xoqFvxqmB\"><strong>今天 12:13</strong></a></cite>&nbsp;<strong>来自</strong><cite><a href=\"http://weibo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">新浪微博</a></cite></div>\n<div class=\"rt\" style=\"float: right;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><strong>转发</strong><strong>(1707)</strong></a>&nbsp;<span class=\"MIB_line_l\" style=\"color: #d4d4d4;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 9px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 8px\">|</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><strong>收藏</strong></a>&nbsp;<span class=\"MIB_line_l\" style=\"color: #d4d4d4;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 9px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 8px\">|</span>&nbsp;<a id=\"_comment_count_miniblog2_3358223897966169\" href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><strong>评论</strong><strong>(626</strong></a></div>\n</div>\n<p></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #444444;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height: 22px;background-color: #d0f1f6\">@东城区徐春柳：图为区人大的选举指南，上面扯出了一个纯居民的蛋，下图为北京市人大选举法实施细则。明明第一居住地，第二条单位，两条是并列关系，是供选民选择的。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #444444;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height: 22px;background-color: #d0f1f6\">书记跟我讲，如果我一定要在社区参选，有两个办法，一个是把工作辞掉，失业在家，一个是说服我的单位不参加选举，请注意，不是我不在单位参选，是我的单位退出选举，请问我如何说服我几千人的单位退选？</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #444444;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;line-height: 22px;background-color: #d0f1f6\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;line-height: normal\"></p>\n<p class=\"sms\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 6px;padding-left: 0px;line-height: 22px;font-size: 14px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">很多人在指责提&ldquo;纯居民&rdquo;概念的居委会书记，其实她不过是被扔出来的一个棋子，是可以牺牲掉的，到时候责任会推给她，只说她理解不到位。所以可鄙的是躲在她后面的东城区人大，想用申诉程序时间玩死我，让我没有办法进入下一步程序。我没有时间陪他们玩，我有更直接的手段。</p>\n<div class=\"MIB_assign\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 5px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;width: 474px;clear: both;padding: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<div class=\"MIB_assign\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 5px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;width: 474px;clear: both;padding: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<div class=\"MIB_assign_c MIB_txtbl\">\n<div class=\"blogPicOri\" style=\"clear: both;text-align: center;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 6px;padding-left: 0px;text-align: left;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><cite><a href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><img class=\"small_icon cls quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />收起</a> <cite class=\"MIB_line_l\">|</cite> </cite><cite><a href=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/53998985tw1dl77z1jjxaj.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"small_icon original quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />查看大图</a> </cite><cite class=\"MIB_line_l\">|</cite> <cite><a id=\"left131615891692782387\" href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><img class=\"small_icon turn_l quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />向左转</a> </cite><cite><a id=\"right131615891692790171\" class=\"last_turn_r\" href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><img class=\"small_icon turn_r quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />向右转</a></cite></p>\n<p><img class=\"imgSmall quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/53998985tw1dl77z1jjxaj.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feed_att MIB_linkbl MIB_txtbl\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;color: #707070;clear: both;width: 560px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<div class=\"lf\" style=\"float: left;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><cite><a href=\"http://weibo.com/1402571141/xorChxb74\"><strong>50分钟前</strong></a></cite>&nbsp;<strong>来自</strong><cite><a href=\"http://weibo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">新浪微博</a></cite></div>\n<div class=\"rt\" style=\"float: right;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><strong>转发</strong><strong>(167)</strong></a>&nbsp;<span class=\"MIB_line_l\" style=\"color: #d4d4d4;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 9px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 8px\">|</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><strong>收藏</strong></a>&nbsp;<span class=\"MIB_line_l\" style=\"color: #d4d4d4;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 9px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 8px\">|</span>&nbsp;<a id=\"_comment_count_miniblog2_3358260337907546\" href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><strong>评论</strong><strong>(112)</strong></a></div>\n</div>\n<p></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #707070;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;line-height: 20px;background-color: #d0f1f6\"></p>\n<p class=\"source\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 6px;padding-left: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><a href=\"http://weibo.com/2163996325\">@二哥二世</a>：【忠实里2】高个子主任明确告诉我，有单位的一律要在单位进行选民登记，并且指着&ldquo;致本区选民的一封信&rdquo;上的字样逐行读给我，语气中没有商量的余地。关于选区划分，她说忠实里社区因为比较大，就是一个独立的选区。每个选区选民登记的最后日期稍有不同，夕照寺是10.4，忠实里是9.30。<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E4%B8%9C%E5%9F%8E%E5%8C%BA%E5%BE%90%E6%98%A5%E6%9F%B3\">@东城区徐春柳</a></p>\n<div class=\"blogPicOri\" style=\"clear: both;text-align: center;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<div class=\"blogPicOri\" style=\"clear: both;text-align: center;padding: 0px;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\">\n<p style=\"padding-top: 10px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 6px;padding-left: 0px;text-align: left;margin: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\"><cite><a href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><img class=\"small_icon cls quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />收起</a> <cite class=\"MIB_line_l\">|</cite> </cite><cite><a href=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/80fbf6a5gw1dl6br2i21oj.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"small_icon original quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />查看大图</a> </cite><cite class=\"MIB_line_l\">|</cite> <cite><a id=\"left131615879140969629\" href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><img class=\"small_icon turn_l quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />向左转</a> </cite><cite><a id=\"right131615879140961616\" class=\"last_turn_r\" href=\"http://weibo.com/jpg46\"><img class=\"small_icon turn_r quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images//common/transparent.gif\" alt=\"\" />向右转</a></cite></p>\n<p><img class=\"imgSmall quimby_search_image\" src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/80fbf6a5gw1dl6br2i21oj.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</div>\n<p></span></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[20534],"tags":[16824,9729]}